---
import SiteLayout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/home/Hero.astro";
import heroImage from "../assets/hero.png";
---

<SiteLayout
  title="Creando Spark — Creando Futuronan"
  description="A space for the restless ones. Where code, art, and AI collide."
>
  <Hero
    headline="Creando Spark (12–18)"
    sub="A space for the restless ones. Where code, art, and AI crash into each other and something new sparks."
    ctas={[
      { label: "Apply / Register", href: "#apply" },
      { label: "FAQs", href: "#faq" },
    ]}
    image={heroImage}
  />

  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-10 lg:py-14">
    <div class="prose prose-sm sm:prose lg:prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p>
        <strong>No grades. No gurus.</strong> Just ideas, experiments, and the people
        wild enough to try them.
      </p>
      <p>
        Make weird things. Break boring things. Learn by doing — and unlearning.
      </p>

      <h2 class="h2 mt-10">About the programme</h2>
      <p>
        Join us for <strong>4 creative Saturday sessions</strong> where we’ll play
        with coding, AI, communication networks, and digital design — no boring lectures,
        no prior experience needed. We learn by asking questions, using our own culture
        and experiences as the starting point, and working together as a community.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Focus:</strong> creative coding, AI, digital culture, storytelling,
          communication networks, design
        </li>
        <li><strong>Schedule:</strong> Saturdays — 8, 15, 22, 29 November</li>
        <li><strong>Approach:</strong> experiment, collaborate, remix</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10">Methodologies</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Contextual Design:</strong> We start from what’s around us — our
        stories, materials, surroundings.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Popular Education:</strong> Everyone’s a teacher, everyone’s a learner.
        Curiosity is the curriculum.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Radical Data:</strong> Follow your sparks; prototype to test the
        impossible.
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="team">Team</h3>
      <p>
        Co-hosted by Radical Data, Plataforma Aruba, Metabolic Foundation,
        Counter/Narratives & Afaina de Jong. See <a href="/about#partners"
          >partners →</a
        >
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10">Location</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>RAA! (Residencia Artistico Aruba)</strong><br />Caya Betico
        Croes 110, Oranjestad, Aruba
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10">Language</h3>
      <p>Sessions in English, with support in Papiamento and Spanish.</p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="info">Info sessions</h3>
      <p>
        If you want to join Spark, come to our <strong
          >info sessions for parents and guardians</strong
        > on <strong>Sat 11 Oct</strong> and <strong>Sat 18 Oct</strong> — <strong
          >10:00–14:00</strong
        > at <strong>RAA!</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        WhatsApp: <a
          href="https://wa.me/2975689420"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">+297 568 9420</a
        >
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="apply">Apply / Register</h3>
      <p>Ready to join? Tap the button below.</p>
      <p>
        <a
          href="#apply"
          class="btn-primary btn-md"
          style="background: var(--color-accent);">Apply to Spark</a
        >
        <a href="#faq" class="btn-outline btn-md ml-2">Read FAQs</a>
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="apply" href="#apply">Apply / Register</h3>
      <p>
        Interested in joining? Write on WhatsApp to: <a
          href="https://wa.me/2975689420"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">+297 568 9420</a
        >
      </p>

      <h3 class="h3 mt-10" id="faq">FAQs</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Who can join?</strong> Young people aged 12–18, based in Aruba.
      </p>
      <p><strong>Do I need prior experience?</strong> Nope — just curiosity.</p>
      <p>
        <strong>Is there a cost?</strong> Participation is free; materials provided.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Where are sessions held?</strong> All sessions happen at RAA! in
        Oranjestad.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>How do I apply?</strong> Message us on WhatsApp to start the process.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</SiteLayout>
